name: Paneer Biryani
description: A super delicious and aromatic Indian rice entree made using fragrant basmati rice, cubes of paneer (Indian cottage cheese) and spices. Biryani Served with Salan, Raita and Salad.

name: Tandoori Chicken
description: Juicy chicken marinated in a combination of flavourful spices and roasted to perfection in tandoor. (Served with chutney And Salad). (1 chest piece, 1 leg piece of chicken served )

name: Chicken Tikka
description: Super soft chunks of chicken are coated with a spicy and peppery masala and grilled to perfection. (Served with chutney And Salad)

name: Chicken Biryani Single
description: Aromatic rice preparation layered with marinated chicken pieces and spices slow-cooked to perfection. Serves one. (Biryani Served with Chicken 1 pc, Salan, Raita and Salad)

name: Chicken Biryani Regular
description: Aromatic rice preparation layered with marinated chicken pieces and spices slow-cooked to perfection. Serves 2. (Biryani Served with Chicken 2 pc, Salan, Raita and Salad)

name: Mutton Biryani
description: Wholesome biryani prepared with succulent mutton, aromatic basmati biryani rice and whole spices. (Biryani Served with Mutton 6 pc, Egg, Salan, Raita and Salad)

name: Istah's Chicken Shawarma Rumali
description: (100% Halal & Breast Boneless Chicken) Fresh rumali loaded with diced chicken (contains more chicken instead of onions). Loaded with egg based garlic mayonnaise & with a touch of in-house sauce.

name: Paneer Shawarma
description: Fresh rumali loaded with grilled paneer & salad. Loaded with egg based garlic mayonnaise & with a touch of in-house sauce
